'''霍夫斯冰原'''（{{lang-is|Hofsjökull}}）位于[[冰岛|冰岛]]中部，面积925 km<sup>2</sup>，为冰岛第三大[[冰川|冰川]]，最高点海拔1765米<ref>{{Citation | last = National Land Survey of Iceland | title = National Land Survey of Iceland – Geographical information | url = http://www.lmi.is/english/iceland-in-statistics/ | year = 2001 | accessdate = 2008-08-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100406053831/http://www.lmi.is/english/iceland-in-statistics/ | archivedate = 2010-04-06 }}</ref>。霍夫斯冰原是冰岛众多河流的发源地，包括冰岛最长的河流[[肖尔索河|肖尔索河]]<ref>Thordarson & Hoskuldsson, p. 83</ref>。

